This is a code that creates a Lucene benchmark. In order to run, the build file can be used using the ant command.
Code Structure: The main class is in the benchmark.harness package. The name of the class is Benchmark. 
The class Indexer in the package benchmark.indexing is used to create an index. It creates an in-memory index using RAMDirectory. 
The class SearchEngine in the package benchmark.searching is used to search for documents. 

The example can be looked from - http://javatechniques.com/blog/lucene-in-memory-text-search-example/


CREATED BY: Ravi Tandon

